      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or smudge in sight! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
