    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a day of rain or snow. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like gloss with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last season; you will find zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state. The premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the original factory floor mats are pristine, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership, and I have a comprehensive binder of every receipt and inspection report since mile one. It features a smooth, responsive transmission and a quiet, powerful engine that has been treated only to premium synthetic fluids. All electronics, buttons, and driver-assist features function perfectly. Sale includes both original master keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
